# ğŸŒ **Alternative: Deploy to GCP GKE**

```groovy
stage('Deploy to GKE') {
    steps {
        sh '''
            gcloud auth activate-service-account --key-file=$GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS
            gcloud container clusters get-credentials YOUR_CLUSTER --zone asia-south1 --project YOUR_PROJECT
            kubectl apply -f k8s/
        '''
    }
}
```

